						               													<description>Overview&amp;#10;Take on the role of new students at the College of Crawlwell and prepare for an enchanted education full of excitement. Students will face typical school challenges such as rivalries, exams and homework, but add in a magical school full of animated objects, traps, and the lure of the many secrets waiting to be discovered. To graduate they will need to keep their head on straight or at least keep it on all together.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Objective:&amp;#10;The objective of the game is to improve your skills, collect resources, and prepare for the final challenge at the end of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Winning Condition:&amp;#10;The player that scores the most points in the final challenge wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How the game works:&amp;#10;The game board features a map with many locations. A deck of encounter cards is shuffled and 9 cards are revealed. Players will spend their turn moving around the board to either collect or resolve these encounters, perform special location actions, or attempt to sabotage the other players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At the start of the game, each player chooses a Major which is a deck of cards the players will use to improve their character throughout the game as players earn experience for resolving encounters.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is divided into 15 rounds which involve each player taking a turn. At the end of round 15, players will attempt to defeat a series of Dungeon challenges representing the final exam. Players are scored on how well they perform and the player with the highest score wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
